import React from 'react'
import SideBar from './Components/SideBar'
import SearchResult from './Pages/SearchResult'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <BrowserRouter>
        <SideBar />
        <Routes>
          <Route element={<SearchResult />} path="/" />
        </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
